vernac_cmds: Lemma prime_div_or_gcd1 : forall (p : nat) (a : Z), Prime p -> ZDivides (Z_of_nat p) a \/ gcd (Z_of_nat p) a 1.
Lemma divmultgcd : forall a b c : Z, a <> 0%Z -> ZDivides a (b * c) -> gcd a b 1 -> ZDivides a c.
Lemma primedivmult : forall p n m : nat, Prime p -> Divides p (n * m) -> Divides p n \/ Divides p m.
Lemma mod_mult_inv_r : forall (a : Z) (p : nat), Prime p -> ~ Mod a 0 p -> exists ra : Z, Mod (a * ra) 1 p.
Lemma mod_mult_cancel_r : forall (a b c : Z) (p : nat), Prime p -> ~ Mod c 0 p -> Mod (a * c) (b * c) p -> Mod a b p.
Lemma mod_mult_0 : forall (p : nat) (a b : Z), Prime p -> Mod (a * b) 0 p -> Mod a 0 p \/ Mod b 0 p.
Lemma mod_not_exp_0 : forall p : nat, Prime p -> forall a : Z, ~ Mod a 0 p -> forall m : nat, ~ Mod (Exp a m) 0 p.
elim (mod_mult_0 p a (Exp a n) Hp).
Lemma techlemma3 : forall (qlist : natlist) (a b : nat), 0 < a -> a < b -> Divides a b -> b = product qlist -> allPrime qlist -> exists qi : nat, inlist nat qi qlist /\ Divides a (multDrop qi qlist).

command: elim (mod_mult_0 p a (Exp a n) Hp).
